          I have gone through the extended toil of making sure that this birthday spectacular is one for the ages.
          Below, you will be faced with a series of Herculean tasks designed to make you fail.
          If you somehow find a way to pass all these tests, you will (probably) be rewarded accordingly.
        </p>
        <p>
